 "Title":"Prohibits the sale of playground surfacing materials that contain PFAS, PAHs or more than ninety parts per million of lead; and provides penalties for violations",
 "Summary":"Prohibits the sale of playground surfacing materials that contain PFAS, PAHs or lead; prevents sellers of playground surfacing materials that contain PFAS, PAHs or lead from being held in violation when relying in good faith on a certificate of compliance provided by the manufacturer; provides penalties for violations.",
 "LawSection":"Environmental Conservation Law","LawCode":"Add §37-0123, amd §71-3703, En Con L",
 "ActClause":"AN ACT to amend the environmental conservation law, in relation to the regulation of toxic substances in playground surfacing materials",
 "SameAsPrintNo":"S3852-2025","PreviousVersions":["S8932-2023"]
}